title: Steve Jobs ready for its national box office reveal
text:
'Steve Jobs' ready for its national box office reveal 
CNN Money Saturday 24th October, 2015 
The Universal biopic about the eccentric Apple founder has pulled in roughly $2.3 million in its limited theatrical run, but now the film will expand from 60 theaters to over 2,400 this weekend....
